$game.master.name has invited you to play a game of Trivolous!

Trivolous is a social trivia game, but it's not your typical trivia game because the questions are created by you and the other players.  The goal is to make questions that all the players can answer.  Any topic or subject is possible (even about the other players) and it only takes a minute a day to play. 

Playing Trivolous is a fun way to keep in touch with your friends and family!

The name of this game is '${game.name}' and this is what it's about: '${game.description}'

Go here to accept or decline the invitation : ${baseUrl}?email=${member.email}

You can email the game master, ( ${game.master.email}?Subject=Trivolous%20Registration ) with any questions (like is this spam? It really isn't).

After you register, you will be able to view the instructions and FAQ for more details.
 
Thanks and have fun playing!

